    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……\n莉央さん、決まりました！　決まりましたよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huff‚ huff…\nRio-san‚ it’s decided! It’s decided!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、何をそんなに興奮してるの？\n慌てるなんて、貴方らしくないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ what are you so excited about?\nYou’re not usually flustered like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2280274749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "まずは汗を拭きなさい。レッスン中の私より汗だくよ\nもう……用事なら、電話かメッセで良かったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wipe your sweat first. You're sweating more than me during practice.\nGeez… You could've just called or texted me if you had something to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6946941416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません\n重大なことですし、直接伝えたいと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry.\nI wanted to tell you in person because it's important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6666665752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい。で、どうしたの？\nその様子だと、大きな仕事でも決まったのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ alright. So‚ what’s up?\nJudging by your reaction‚ did you land a big job?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9884819706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりライブ？　それともCMかしら\n地上波のCMなら、確かに大きな仕事よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it a live performance after all? Or a commercial?\nIf it’s a commercial on a terrestrial channel‚ it’s definitely a big deal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.8551486373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "年末の例の番組に、LizNoir出演確定です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s confirmed that LizNoir will appear on that year-end program!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7551485101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ふうん、そうなの。私達が年末のあの番組に\n出演が決まった――って、え！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ is that so. We’ve been confirmed\nto appear on that year-end program… Huh?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8208239913,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}